thumb|300px|aerial view of whakarewarewa ; pohutu geyser is erupting whakarewarewa ( reduced version of te whakarewarewatanga o te ope taua a wahiao , meaning the gathering place for the war parties of wahiao , often abbreviated to whaka by locals ) is a geothermal area within rotorua city in the taupo volcanic zone of new zealand .

world travel : bubbling mud pools , erupting geysers , & maori song & dance will delight you at whakarewarewa in this country

